beer.beer_description:
Velvet smooth, Rogers' Beer weaves together the best whole hop flowers and toasted malts into a silky mid strength ale like no other. 

Style: Amber Ale

Malt: 
Pale Malt, Wheat, Carapils, Vienna

Hops: 
East Kent Goldings (UK) used in the kettle, Cascade pellets (US/AUS/NZ) in the whirlpool with Stella (AUS) and Cascade (US/AUS) whole hop cones used in the hop back. 

Pairing: 
Big hearty dishes such as goulash, slow cooked casseroles and meats.
